1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,200
Science has a clearer story about microbiome antibiotics impact than social media does.

2
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:09,600
Antibiotics save lives but can disrupt gut bacteria, our microbiome's ecosystem.

3
00:00:09,600 --> 00:00:14,000
This disruption may lead to digestive issues, allergies, and even obesity!

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:18,800
Studies show a link between antibiotics and reduced diversity in gut bacteria.

5
00:00:18,800 --> 00:00:23,200
But not all antibiotics affect everyone the same way—individual responses vary.

6
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:25,600
Want to keep your microbiome healthy?

7
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:28,000
Talk to your doctor about antibiotics.
